Interface STView

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.apache.sling.api.adapter.Adaptable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    TransitorySTView

    public interface STView
extends org.apache.sling.api.adapter.Adaptable
    A representation of a single view node with methods to get and set all of the attributes of the view

    mck
